# Domain-specific routing
https://www.soltecsol.com/*    /company-home.html   200
https://app.soltecsol.com/success    /success.html   200
https://app.soltecsol.com/cancel     /index.html     200

# Stripe success/cancel redirects
/success    /success.html   200
/cancel     /index.html     200

# API routes to Netlify Functions
/api/*      /.netlify/functions/:splat   200

# SPA fallback for client-side routing
/*          /index.html     200